1
00:01:56,326 --> 00:01:58,028
Varje år är den stora eventet i familjens liv hela världen sin nya automobil.

2
00:01:58,067 --> 00:01:59,989
Det är inte att familjens bil behöver förändras, utan att varje år är bilarna fintare.

3
00:02:25,818 --> 00:02:29,123
Bilarna är säkrare, snabbare och mer ekonomiska.

4
00:02:30,365 --> 00:02:31,366
Vad gör det möjligt?

5
00:02:32,288 --> 00:02:35,772
Hur kan bilarna bli bättre varje år?

6
00:02:35,853 --> 00:02:39,957
Ansvaret till den frågan är en drama som skapas bakom scenen där en ny bil är skapad.

7
00:02:43,579 --> 00:02:52,143
Story begins in the division for customer research, where a close check is kept on what the automobile buyer wants in his next car.

8
00:02:53,062 --> 00:03:00,545
Thousands of questionnaires, field reports and surveys help the designers to anticipate public needs and desires.

9
00:03:01,986 --> 00:03:08,770
The new model of today is the result of engineering research, or testing new metals and new construction.

10
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:19,324
Those car manufacturers who enjoy the advantages of this central research organization have an invaluable source of knowledge for keeping their products truly up to date.

11
00:03:20,003 --> 00:03:26,246
Each factory adds to the findings of the parent institution that results of special studies in their own laboratories.

12
00:03:27,066 --> 00:03:34,769
They study the strains and stresses in new gear designs or examine the effects of new materials for brake drums and lining.

13
00:03:38,126 --> 00:03:42,968
In the art and color division of General Motors, new body designs are created in clay.

14
00:03:43,769 --> 00:03:51,432
These new models combine the latest trends in styling with the engineers specifications for overall size and riding comfort.

15
00:03:54,054 --> 00:04:04,120
At the central proving grounds, each General Motors car division has its own staff for putting new designs to exacting tests, checking performance, economy, safety.

16
00:04:05,725 --> 00:04:10,031
Durabilitet och frihet av operationen.

17
00:04:10,050 --> 00:04:14,355
Det tar ett kombinerat arbete av många människor för att skapa ett nytt modell.

18
00:04:14,376 --> 00:04:19,122
Allt detta arbete är koncentrerat och koordinerat i fabriksingenjörsdepartementet.

19
00:04:19,161 --> 00:04:23,406
Ingenjörerna är männen som har blivit ansvariga för att hålla produktledarskapet i sitt område.

20
00:04:27,170 --> 00:04:28,370
Allt måste förstås börja med en idé.

21
00:04:28,391 --> 00:04:32,173
Och chefträffaren ser att dessa idéer skapas på papper här i träningsrummet.

22
00:04:32,194 --> 00:04:35,415
Den här stora bilden säkerställer att allt kommer att finnas när jobbet är samlat.

23
00:04:35,435 --> 00:04:37,596
Från dessa bilder skapas verkliga modeller av samma material som kommer att användas i produktionen.

24
00:04:52,995 --> 00:04:56,862
And the new car begins to take shape almost as soon as the drawings are made.

25
00:04:58,021 --> 00:05:02,521
Mekanikerna i ingenjörsdepartementet uttrycker bilderna till metall.

26
00:05:02,581 --> 00:05:14,185
Ingenjörerna arbetar med tillverkare för att se till att alla nya delar är praktiska från en tillverkningspunkt, så att de kan bytas och samlas i kvalitetsproduktion.

27
00:05:14,225 --> 00:05:18,346
Varje ingenjör är ansvarig för designen och kvaliteten av en definitiv del av bilen.

28
00:05:18,865 --> 00:05:24,086
Han följer den hela tiden, från början på papperet, till att det är samlat i den fina bilen.

29
00:05:26,482 --> 00:05:27,968
These cars are all tailor-made.

30
00:05:28,471 --> 00:05:30,942
Each new part is handwork from the master drawing.

31
00:05:35,875 --> 00:05:38,916
Some of these men have been on the job for over 25 years.

32
00:05:39,336 --> 00:05:43,278
And that holds true in all the manufacturing divisions of this great institution.

33
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:46,439
Now let's see what some of the engineers themselves are doing.

34
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:51,781
The electrical engineer has to keep up to date on everything from spark plugs to radio.

35
00:05:52,622 --> 00:05:55,423
Cars must withstand the extremes of all climates.

36
00:05:55,942 --> 00:06:01,185
This engineer wants to see if a new engine will start at below zero temperatures.

37
00:06:03,004 --> 00:06:05,625
And if it will start here, it will start anywhere.

38
00:06:05,644 --> 00:06:16,430
The supervisor of the dynamometer room has been running this new engine at top speed for 200 hours because he wants to find out how much longer it will run before something goes wrong.

39
00:06:16,990 --> 00:06:20,773
Back in the factory, the body engineer and his men are working with wooden models.

40
00:06:21,192 --> 00:06:24,154
They use these models in making final improvements in the body.

41
00:06:24,175 --> 00:06:27,656
The executive engineer is really the business manager.

42
00:06:28,076 --> 00:06:31,598
He heads the experimental shops and also has charge of personnel.

43
00:06:32,673 --> 00:06:33,935
Vi är sist en chefingenjör.

44
00:06:33,954 --> 00:06:38,778
Här är det byggd jobb av keeping fängs workings modell i en efficient leg by koordinering.

45
00:06:38,798 --> 00:06:39,660
Det verkar bestämt.

46
00:06:40,379 --> 00:06:48,706
En i charge av det inta departement responsible för all the work that is done there is the chief engineer after all of the designing has been finished.

47
00:06:49,168 --> 00:06:54,632
All the tests run in the new parts, the tools and dies made up the new model is put into production.

48
00:06:54,651 --> 00:06:58,615
The manufacturing division has stalled the world for the finest materials.

49
00:08:03,745 --> 00:08:07,709
Manufacturing methods have kept pace with every step of engineering progress.

50
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:10,892
Better, more efficient machines have been developed.

51
00:08:12,014 --> 00:08:22,062
Finer automatic tools, precision equipment, more sensitive checking and measuring instruments in the hands of experienced workmen control the quality of every part.

52
00:08:23,122 --> 00:08:35,065
Men historien av alla dessa metoder och av alla saker som hände bakom sidan är bara en förslag till den stora historien varje marknadsdivision av General Motors har att berätta om.

53
00:08:35,085 --> 00:08:36,424
Den historien av sin egen nya produkt.
